doc.after: Physical geography also known as geosystems or physiography is one of the two major sub fields of geography 1 Physical geography is that branch of natural science which deals with the study of processes and patterns in the natural environment like the atmosphere hydrosphere biosphere and geosphere as opposed to the cultural or built environment the domain of human geography
